U[5]:
1:Teams-first multi-agent orchestration in Claude Code with zero config
2:Parallel agent execution with persistent verify/fix loops (ralph)
3:Guaranteed-completion tasks with Guarantee→Enhancement→Execution skill layers
4:3-model synthesis with Codex+Gemini+Claude (CCG mode)
