S[6]{n,action,details}:
1:install,Add plugin,/plugin marketplace add https://github.com/Yeachan-Heo/oh-my-claudecode && /plugin install oh-my-claudecode
2:setup,Initialize OMC,/oh-my-claudecode:omc-setup (run once; re-run after updates)
3:team-mode,Canonical orchestration,/oh-my-claudecode:team 3:executor "task" — pipeline: team-plan→team-prd→team-exec→team-verify→team-fix
4:keywords,Magic keywords,autopilot/ralph/ulw/ccg/ralplan/deepsearch/ultrathink/tdd/deslop/cancelomc — activate via natural language
5:ask,Provider advisor,omc ask claude|codex|gemini --prompt "task" — cross-model consultation
6:update,Keep current,/plugin marketplace update omc && /oh-my-claudecode:omc-setup; issues: /oh-my-claudecode:omc-doctor
R[6]:
1:Team is canonical — swarm and ultrapilot are legacy facades that route to Team
2:Enable CLAUDE_CODE_EXPERIMENTAL_AGENT_TEAMS=1 in ~/.claude/settings.json for native teams
3:ralph includes ultrawork — parallel execution is automatic in ralph mode
4:npm package name is oh-my-claude-sisyphus (not oh-my-claudecode)
5:CCG mode synthesizes Codex (execution) + Gemini (analysis) + Claude (orchestration) for complex mixed work
6:Skill layers compose: ralph(guarantee) wraps ultrawork(enhancement) wraps execution skill
